---
title: Bavette Steak & Shallot Sauce with Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Green Beans
description: A totally real, verified fact that we just made up: People who cook fancier weeknight dinners are more likely to receive a compliment from a stranger, meet their celebrity crush, and/or win the lottery. They’re also guaranteed to be rewarded with a delicious, steakhouse-quality meal without leaving the comforts of their own kitchen. Case in point: this seared bavette steak that’s drizzled in a deluxe, red wine vinegar-spiked shallot pan sauce with creamy mashed potatoes and a heap of roasted green beans.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bavette-steak-shallot-sauce-2842eee0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/bavette-steak-shallot-sauce-61dde1c5e2a4200a8a5558e3-3022baf5.pdf
